{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_017ZADakquFtW4xbxtWhcNNQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me begin the migration. The key changes needed:\n\n1. **Jakarta EE on Open Liberty** -> **Quarkus** \n2. **EJB (@Singleton, @Stateful)** -> **CDI beans (@ApplicationScoped, @RequestScoped)**\n3. **JSF (Faces/XHTML)** -> **JAX-RS REST endpoints** (Quarkus doesn't support JSF natively)\n4. **JPA persistence.xml with JTA** -> **Quarkus datasource in application.properties**\n5. **Liberty server.xml** -> removed\n6. **WAR packaging** -> **JAR packaging**\n\nLet me start with the pom.xml:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":533,"cache_read_input_tokens":48991,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":533,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":635},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"9c218712-4305-4391-b809-2a32cfe389f4","uuid":"83cfc378-b004-4d34-9be5-e519866d7168"}
